title: Poser ~ DAZ3D : Dodge Street Van 1976-1980 [RO 104517]
description:
Highly detailed character for Poser7 and greater.
 Tested without problem in DazStudio.

 MANY OPTIONAL PARTS ARE AVAILABLE. THESE PARTS ARE HIDDEN WHEN YOU IMPORT THE CHARACTER.JUST SELECT THE PARTS YOU WANT TO SHOW OR HIDE:
 A FIBERHOOD ( hide the standard HOOD)
 4 WHEELARCHES
 A FRONT SPOILER
 A ROOF SPOILER
 ZOOMIES EXHAUSTS ( choose the EXHAUST you want to show )
 SIDEPIPES EXHAUSTS ( choose the EXHAUST you want to show )
 4 DIFFERENT WINDOWS ON THE LEFT SIDE ( choose the window you want to show )
 4 DIFFERENT WINDOWS ON THE RIGHT SIDE ( choose the window you want to show )
 3 DIFFERENT KIND OF RIMS ( choose the rim you want to show )

 
https://pximg.xyz/images/f9a5e127206a97237380bd83ba7b0f70.jpg


Renderosity 104517 - Dodge Street Van 1976-1980

Note:
What was intended as a reflection map is often used as the diffuse map, so many parts look awful out of the box. Just swap it over to the proper channel. Adjust the body colour with the diffuse channels or make your own
